criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  aged ≥ 19 years;

          -  android smartphone users;

          -  no changes in medication for diabetes for at least 6 months;

          -  HbA1c levels ≥6.5% within the last 3 months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  currently had serious concomitant disease other than diabetes (n=1);
             malignancy-related histories on admission, myocardial infarction, cerebral infarction
             or organ transplantation;

          -  pregnant or had plans for pregnancy within 6 months;

          -  plans to participate in other clinical studies or illiteracy.
